Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.37,0:00:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.50,0:00:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那借来的写轮眼能抵挡这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你见识下真品与盗版的差距吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.17,0:00:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.48,0:00:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 她怎么过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.55,0:00:48.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.56,0:00:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能让卡卡西老师背负一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.75,0:00:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你们不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走的不是一条道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.32,0:00:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们一起努力过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.15,0:01:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经认为那就是自己该走的路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.42,0:01:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.28,0:01:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是决意踏上复仇之路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此我才活到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.61,0:01:15.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法像你和鸣人那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了佐助什么都愿意做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:21.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…求求你 留下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:23.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会帮你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.34,0:01:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会想尽一切办法帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以请你和我一起留下…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.91,0:01:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果实在不行 就带我一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.96,0:01:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然…很讨人厌
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.80,0:01:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,否则我就喊人了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来的真是时候啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你能过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.60,0:05:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之多亏你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.28,0:05:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢了 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助真的打算杀我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.77,0:05:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果鸣人没有赶来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在我已经被佐助亲手杀死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.60,0:05:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱同是第七班的成员啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.88,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说是曾经的第七班…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 小樱 你们现在应该明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.09,0:05:50.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他身上浮现的是真正的杀气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.66,0:05:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经不是曾经的佐助了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.28,0:06:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听阿飞那家伙说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:30.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鼬的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.66,0:06:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道那家伙说的是真是假
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.47,0:06:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不管怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.57,0:06:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所做的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.57,0:06:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.15,0:06:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前就说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.87,0:07:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既没父母也没兄弟的你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我的理解能有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外人给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道鸣人是怎么对你的吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论什么流言蜚语
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他都一直视你为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:18.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便大家都准备对付佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:23.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人还是一心想着救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.64,0:07:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是现在…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想救我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么救…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.27,0:07:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.85,0:07:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我绝对要把你…从复仇的泥泞中拯救出来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.53,0:07:47.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那个必要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的复仇帷幕已经拉开了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在刚才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手刃了一个鼬的仇人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:06.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了得到那只右手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.98,0:08:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你杀害了多少宇智波族人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出手的是鼬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你逼他的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是里四象封印术
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 快远离团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这干掉了木叶的高层
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:47.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫团藏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.21,0:08:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助难道仅凭一人就打倒他了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.80,0:08:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止 从未有过的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:09:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被玷污的宇智波得到净化的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:05.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宇智波从这腐朽的忍者世界超脱的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是无法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.09,0:09:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.14,0:09:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某种意义上来说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.30,0:09:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是你们木叶长久以来的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如你们所愿 让亘古以来一直被否定的宇智波
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你们的记忆中消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木叶的一切…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.44,0:09:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斩断同木叶所有的羁绊才是净化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是宇智波的真正复兴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.99,0:09:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:47.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那憎恨累积而成的历史
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,造就了现在的佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.84,0:09:56.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助也是这个时代的受害者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.87,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人也好 小樱也好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.71,0:10:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽不能确定 但多少也能察觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.23,0:10:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.24,0:10:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 小樱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都给我离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是 卡卡西老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,留在这里会看到不愿看到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.56,0:10:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在离开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.38,0:11:00.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小樱 从静音那学来的毒苦无是杀不掉佐助的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他继承了大蛇丸的免疫力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 你已经清楚自己的心意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我已经帮你恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.21,0:11:22.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你的身体…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.57,0:11:26.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续战斗可不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要动 香燐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:54.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同人质的要害一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么做啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 这是第一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罢了 佐助的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡卡西老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓不愿看到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.55,0:12:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杀了佐助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.78,0:12:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有破绽 我可不会手下留情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助 或许…我和你…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.26,0:13:57.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该反过来才对…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不断地逃啊 逃啊 苟且偷生下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后当有一天你拥有跟我相同的眼睛后
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来找我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千鸟 螺旋丸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.10,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.65,0:15:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.09,0:15:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经被村民们厌恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是因为我体内的九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:32.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经也憎恨村里的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也曾想过报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些涂鸦给我擦干净
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.31,0:15:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那小子 就是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.43,0:15:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要将这种家伙留在村子里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三代替我们想想就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.92,0:16:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋 滚一边去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么突然来一下你要干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你好了 赶紧给我滚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:22.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 到底为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.19,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都这样对我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.82,0:16:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就连班主任也用这种眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不是扫把星或霉菌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.65,0:16:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我是漩涡鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果稍有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.46,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就会像你一样想着如此恐怖的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.24,0:17:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾觉得我会一直孤单下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.32,0:17:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到同你和伊鲁卡老师相遇之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.22,0:17:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高次 回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大智 吃晚饭了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.12,0:17:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么不听话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.61,0:17:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说过不准和那个孩子一起玩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.94,0:17:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.72,0:18:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…告诉你真相吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道十二年前封印妖狐的事件吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后村里就有了条规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.24,0:18:40.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是条绝对不能让你知道的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.15,0:18:43.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只对我保密 什么规定…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.09,0:18:51.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不能说出鸣人就是妖狐的规定
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.90,0:18:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说 你就是杀害了伊鲁卡的双亲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.35,0:18:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毁灭村子的九尾妖狐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:06.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所憧憬的第四代火影将九尾封印在你体内
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里所有人都瞒着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会认同你这样的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.69,0:19:16.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.16,0:19:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人 趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.31,0:19:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很寂寞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.91,0:19:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.31,0:19:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果再可靠些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.01,0:20:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不会经历这些痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.28,0:20:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走火入魔般的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.96,0:20:09.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你和伊鲁卡老师 我才得救
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.43,0:20:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当我知道你也总是一人时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你跟我一样我就觉得很安心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.14,0:20:23.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟你都是小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在回想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我背负着九尾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背负着宇智波的宿命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们背负着相似的包袱
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是讽刺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天看到你的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实想去找你聊天的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得你应该能理解我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我还是放弃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要问原因的话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你什么都行 让人羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我决定把你当作我的竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那时起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.75,0:21:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就成了我的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.18,0:22:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐助
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.47,0:22:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.93,0:22:55.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你曾在终结之谷说过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:58.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.87,0:23:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的对决让我终于有所理解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.62,0:23:06.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也读懂我内心的真实想法了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.74,0:23:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.16,0:23:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一流的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.50,0:23:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么对我如此执着
